data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom haven in Elgin! As you step inside, the open living room seamlessly flows into the dining area and kitchen, adorned with granite countertops, a pantry, ample storage and convenient backyard access. The main floor also hosts the inviting primary suite for ultimate convenience. Ascend the stairs to discover an additional seating area, perfect for lounging or creating a vibrant game room atmosphere. All secondary bedrooms and the laundry room are thoughtfully positioned upstairs, ensuring practical living. Outside, the expansive backyard space provides the ideal backdrop for gatherings and celebrations. With its prime location just minutes away from local schools, shopping, and more, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. *Solar panels on the rear of the home. Seller will transfer ownership at closing. Monthly payment is $145.78*
